685
00:56:14,033 --> 00:56:16,200
<c.Japanese>わたくしの借金をチャラに</c.Japanese>

686
00:56:17,566 --> 00:56:20,766
<c.Japanese>それから 以前
手付けでお支払いした5000万<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

687
00:56:21,466 --> 00:56:22,766
<c.Japanese>わたくしに返してください</c.Japanese>

688
00:56:24,133 --> 00:56:25,200
<c.Japanese>これで<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

689
00:56:25,833 --> 00:56:29,466
<c.Japanese>会長と わたくしは
貸し借りなしの五分と五分</c.Japanese>

690
00:56:31,033 --> 00:56:33,033
<c.Japanese>わたくしのことは お忘れください</c.Japanese>

691
00:56:33,233 --> 00:56:34,166
<c.Japanese>フッ</c.Japanese>

692
00:56:34,733 --> 00:56:37,433
<c.Japanese>フフフフフッ…</c.Japanese>

693
00:56:37,533 --> 00:56:40,166
<c.Japanese>お前は やっぱり面白い</c.Japanese>

694
00:56:41,300 --> 00:56:45,000
<c.Japanese>（元子）明日までに 5000万
お振り込みいただけますか</c.Japanese>

695
00:56:49,266 --> 00:56:50,766
<c.Japanese>振込先です</c.Japanese>

696
00:56:52,733 --> 00:56:56,233
<c.Japanese>そんな領収書 あったかどうか<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

697
00:56:58,066 --> 00:57:00,933
<c.Japanese>一晩 ゆっくり考えよう</c.Japanese>

698
00:57:38,333 --> 00:57:40,833
<c.Japanese>（元子）<c.Japanese>領収書は本物だった</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

699
00:57:41,633 --> 00:57:43,600
<c.Japanese>少なくとも あの人は<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

700
00:57:43,700 --> 00:57:46,600
<c.Japanese>本気で 私と
逃げようとしてたんだわ</c.Japanese>

701
00:57:49,566 --> 00:57:52,633
<c.Japanese>（司会）安島</c.Japanese><c.Japanese><c.Japanese>富夫</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>とみお</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese><c.Japanese>先生の</c.Japanese>
