00:57:56,500 --> 00:57:58,833
<c.Japanese>衆議院議員の</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>ナカイコウイチ先生</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese>

704
00:57:58,933 --> 00:58:00,433
<c.Japanese>よろしく</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>お願いいたします</c.Japanese>

705
00:58:00,533 --> 00:58:02,366
<c.Japanese>（出席者たちの拍手）</c.Japanese>

706
00:58:02,466 --> 00:58:05,000
<c.Japanese>（ナカイ）</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>安島君</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>初当選おめでとう</c.Japanese>

707
00:58:05,066 --> 00:58:07,833
<c.Japanese>（ナカイ）万歳！
（一同）万歳！</c.Japanese>

708
00:58:07,933 --> 00:58:10,400
<c.Japanese>（ナカイ）万歳！
（一同）万歳！</c.Japanese>

709
00:58:10,466 --> 00:58:13,433
<c.Japanese>（ナカイ）万歳！
